data.title: Tim Burton's Ed Wood! Still my favorite Burton pic and favorite bio-pic! Johnny Depp stars as legendary driector Ed Wood who became...
data.meta_description:
78 likes, 1 comments - monsterkidstudios on September 28, 2022: "Tim Burton's Ed Wood! Still my favorite Burton pic and favorite bio-pic! Johnny Depp stars as legendary driector Ed Wood who became notorious for being the worst director of all time. He and his films have amassed a huge cult following that I'm sure would disagree with that assessment. The film also stars Martin Landau as Bela Lugosi (the role landed him an Oscar), Bill Murray, Patricia Arquette, Sarah Jessica Parker, Jeffrey Jones as The Amazing Criswell, and George "The Animal" Steele as Tor Johnson.  This film is fun to watch along with the Ed Wood classics Plan 9 From Outer Space and Bride of the Monster.
#edwood #edwoodmovie #edwooddirector #timburton #timburtonsedwood #johnnydepp #billmurray #brideofthemonster #plan9fromouterspace #edwood1994 #belalugosi #martinlandau #martinlandauasbelalugosi".
